Description: FFmpeg audio/video filtering library
Version: 11.14.100
Requires: libswscale >= 9.5.100, libavformat >= 62.12.100, libavcodec >= 62.28.100, libswresample >= 6.3.100, libavutil >= 60.26.100
Requires.private: 
Conflicts:
